    <thetext>In  15.4.1 &quot;The Array Constructor Called as a Function&quot;
and 15.4.2 &quot;The Array Constructor&quot;,
the paragraph begins:
    NOTE When &apos;Array&apos; is called as ...

But, for all other constructors, the corresponding paragraphs are not labelled as notes. For consistency, delete &quot;NOTE&quot;?</thetext>
  </long_desc><long_desc isprivate="0" >
