    <bug_when>2012-11-21 16:47:43 -0800</bug_when>
    <thetext>It probably the other way around.  the other constructors should get marked as notes.  In general, these paragraphs aren&apos;t stating normative requirements but are just an informative restatement of what happens in the actual algorithms.</thetext>
